<plot>Old School: Ultimate X is narrated by Ray Flores, a skatebaord icon. Using the "The Board Gallery" in Venice, California as a backdrop, the documentary features footage of skateborders Tony Alva and Jay Adams as well as various current-day X Games athletes. This documentary takes a look into the history of skateboarding, as well as how it relates to extrem sports of today.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?409542</url></doc>
